{"title":"Docker Compose","date":"2019-05-04T15:42:22.000Z","link":"post/338","categories":["Docker"],"updated":"2019-05-04T10:59:07.933Z","content":"<p>先创建 <code>/usr/local/bin</code> 这个目录</p>\n<h2 id=\"安装\">安装<a href=\"post/338#安装\"></a></h2><figure class=\"highlight shell\"><div><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">curl -L https://github.com/docker/compose/releases/download/1.24.0/docker-compose-`uname -s`-`uname -m` -o /usr/local/bin/docker-compose</span><br><span class=\"line\">chmod +x /usr/local/bin/docker-compose</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>\n<h2 id=\"卸载\">卸载<a href=\"post/338#卸载\"></a></h2><p>直接删除即可</p>\n<h2 id=\"启动容器\">启动容器<a href=\"post/338#启动容器\"></a></h2><p>进入<code>/usr/local/docker/tomcat</code></p>\n<p><strong>缩进符必须是空格</strong></p>\n<p>编写 <code>docker-compose.yml</code> 文件，这个是 <code>Compose</code> 使用的主模板文件。<br><figure class=\"highlight yml\"><div><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"attr\">version:</span> <span class=\"string\">'3'</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"attr\">services:</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"attr\">  tomcat:</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"attr\">    restart:</span> <span class=\"string\">always</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"attr\">    image:</span> <span class=\"string\">tomcat</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"attr\">    container_name:</span> <span class=\"string\">tomcat</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"attr\">    ports:</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"bullet\">      -</span> <span class=\"number\">8090</span><span class=\"string\">:8080</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"attr\">    volumes:</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">\t  <span class=\"bullet\">-</span> <span class=\"string\">[宿主机目录]:[容器目录]</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure></p>\n<p>运行 compose 项目<br><figure class=\"highlight shell\"><div><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">docker-compose up </span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">//守护态运行</span><br><span class=\"line\">docker-compose up  -d</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure></p>\n<h2 id=\"查看日志\">查看日志<a href=\"post/338#查看日志\"></a></h2><figure class=\"highlight shell\"><div><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">docker-compose logs -f 容器name</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>\n<h2 id=\"删除容器\">删除容器<a href=\"post/338#删除容器\"></a></h2><figure class=\"highlight shell\"><div><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">docker-compose down</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>\n","prev":{"title":"Docker日志","link":"post/337"},"next":{"title":"Docker 保存和加载镜像","link":"post/339"},"plink":"https://1056438464.github.io/post/338/","toc":[{"title":"安装","id":"安装","index":"1"},{"title":"卸载","id":"卸载","index":"2"},{"title":"启动容器","id":"启动容器","index":"3"},{"title":"查看日志","id":"查看日志","index":"4"},{"title":"删除容器","id":"删除容器","index":"5"}]}